{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset comprises 115K English dialogue samples, including authentic conversations between real patients and doctors sourced from websites, as well as model-generated dialogues and disease database information.",
    "Fine-tuning with this dataset significantly enhances the models' abilities to understand patient needs and provide recommendations.",
    "• ChatMed Consult Dataset (Zhu and Wang, 2023).",
    "The ChatMed Consult Dataset is a Chinese medical online consultation dataset comprising 549K instructions.",
    "These instructions are divided into real internet medical consultation questions and dialogues generated by the model."
  ]
}